#message:0B:10A
{
[Style Narrate]
[InputOff]Goompa has joined the party!![BR]
[InputOn][Wait][Next]
Press [C-DOWN] to have him store power[BR]
for 500 years at a time.[BR]
[Pause 10]It may not look like he's doing much,[BR]
but trust me on this one![BR]
[Wait][Next]
Depending on the circumstances and[BR]
the waxing of the moon, Goompa can[BR]
do the ALMIGHTY TWERK![BR]
[Wait][Next]
The ALMIGHTY TWERK is a blessing[BR]
only to be seen by certain human[BR]
beings. Brace yourself.[BR]
[wait][Next]
In combat, Goompa has the power of[BR]
the death stare.[BR]
[Pause 15]He will judge your every move and[BR]
commit perjury of your wrongdoings.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Goompa is so powerful that he only[BR]
gets a little bit of screen time.[BR]
[Pause 12]He also has a massive forehead, if[BR]
that helps.[Wait][End]
}

