#message:0B:10D
{
[Style Narrate]
[InputOff]Goompa has left the party...[BR]
[InputOn][Wait][Next]
Wow this sucks. He was the best[BR]
party member too, but now you're[BR]
all alone again. [Wave]Forever alone.[BR]
[/fx]What a loser![BR]
[Wait][Next]
That power you kept storing inside[BR]
of him with [C-DOWN] has gone to waste[BR]
by the way, so all of your efforts[BR]
were for naught.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
He's probably farted all of it out[BR]
by now, so great going, genius.[Wait][End]
}

#message:0B:10E
{
[Style Left]
Ay,[Pause 5] Bro. [Pause 10]You're finally awake.[BR]
[Pause 10]You were trying to cross the [BR]
border, right?[BR]
[Pause 10]Walked right into Bower's ambush?[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Oh well, at least you've come to.[BR]
[Pause 5]You know, Bower is still causing[BR]
problems up there.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
If you don't hurry, the entire[BR]
world is gonna end, Bro![BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#message:0B:10F
{
[Style Left]
